==English==

===Etymology===
Latin [[dexteritas]], from [[dexter]] 'on the right'.

===Noun===
'''dexterity'''
# Skill in performing tasks, especially with the hands.
#: ''Playing computer games can improve your manual '''dexterity'''.''
# An attribute / statistic in a roleplaying game, describing agility
#: ''My character in the game is very lithe, he has a high '''dexterity'''.

